data.description: 4.25% VA assumable loan available!!! Seller will pay up to $5,000.00 in closing costs!!!  Beautiful, spacious home features 5 bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms.  Primary bedroom is on the first floor along with a study, separate dining room, living room with wood burning fireplace, large breakfast room and a spacious kitchen with double ovens! Upstairs features a generously sized family/game room, 4 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms and a separate sitting area or workout space.  Three car garage provides plenty of parking space on this cul-de-sac lot.  This home is nestled on back lot of the neighborhood so the whole backyard fence is made of stunning stone!  Beautifully maintained home with tons of living space indoors and outdoors.
